snippet.title: Finger Derpy Announce Gameplay Trailer iOS/Android Game
snippet.description:
Finger Derpy out now, App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/finger-derpy/id977473798?mt=8
Android/Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MommysBestGames.FingerDerpy
Just in time for all those horse races!
Game screens and Presskit: http://mommysbestgames.com/Presskit/sheet.php?p=finger_derpy
Developer: http://www.mommysbestgames.com
Song excerpt: William Tell overture
